## 04 — Engineering (Backend) (Draft)

### Goal
- Ensure all backend features exist per docs and strictly follow:
  - Route → Controller → Service → Repository
  - Centralized error formatting (`src/lib/errors/errorHandler.ts`)

### Immediate compliance refactors (must-do)
- Refactor any route handlers with DB access into services/repositories (especially public endpoints).

